---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Tagline from '../../components/Tagline.astro';
import ServiceIcon from '../../components/ServiceIcon.astro';
---

<Layout title="Product Development - Wellmade" description="From idea to product. For real. Not a prototype that needs rebuilding. A real product, production-ready from day one.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-primary has-blobs py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <ServiceIcon name="product" class="w-14 h-14 text-accent mb-6" />
      <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-4">Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">Product Development</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80">
        From idea to product. For real.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 mt-4">
        Not a prototype that needs rebuilding. Not a demo that falls apart when you click the wrong button. A real product. Production-ready from day one. Built to evolve.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Why it matters.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Too many projects start with a "prototype" that gets thrown away, then rebuilt "properly" - doubling cost, time, and frustration.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We don't work that way.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        We build the real thing from the start. Solid architecture. Scalable infrastructure. Code that can grow with you. Your MVP isn't a demo - it's version one of your product.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Looks Like -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">What it looks like.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Understanding the problem.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Before code, we dig into what you're actually solving. Who's it for? What pain does it fix? What does success look like?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Building in iterations.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">We ship working software early and often. You see progress. Users give feedback. We adjust. No big reveal after months of silence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Production-grade from day one.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Real infrastructure. Real deployment pipelines. Real monitoring. Not "we'll add that later."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Launching and learning.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">We don't disappear after launch. We watch how it performs, what users do, what breaks. Then we iterate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">What you get.</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-body">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>A working product, deployed and running</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Clean, documented codebase - on your repositories</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Scalable infrastructure - on your cloud accounts</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Deployment pipelines and monitoring</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Knowledge transfer and documentation</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>A team that stays until it's actually done</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who it's for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
            <li>Founders with an idea and a deadline</li>
            <li>Companies launching a new product or feature</li>
            <li>Teams who tried once with another provider and got burned</li>
            <li>Anyone tired of demos that never become real products</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who it's not for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
            <li>"Just build what's in the spec" projects with no room for discovery</li>
            <li>Clients who can't access real users or real feedback</li>
            <li>Fixed-price, fixed-scope expectations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-white/90 mt-6 font-medium">We're happy to talk and figure out if there's a fit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work Together -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">How we work together.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We work in days. Flexible, transparent, no surprises.
      </p>
      <a href="/working-with-us" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary/70 transition-colors group">
        See how we work
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-6">Let's build something.</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Tagline />
</Layout>
